WEBVTT

NOTE
aimx 60-second tour captions. Times match website/media/tour-60s.tape.
Tweak alongside the tape if Sleep values change in the source.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.500
You point one MX record at your VPS.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:13.500
One command. Generates the keys, writes the service, prints the DNS to publish.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:21.500
The CLI signs the message and hands it to the recipient's MX.
Same wire as MCP send_email.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:29.500
Markdown with TOML frontmatter. One file per message. No database.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:37.500
Reply lands. Hook fires. The agent gets a push, not a poll.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:45.500
Twelve MCP tools: list, read, send, reply, mark-read, mailbox CRUD.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:53.500
Reply threads via In-Reply-To. Sent file lands in sent/.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:00:60.000
SMTP for AI agents. No middleman.
